		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:2:1:1"/>
		<identifier rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">faest</identifier>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">Drowned</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
  <p><em>Ostensibly</em> this was going to be a reboot of <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/2/1/0/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::2:1:0"><code>bjmns:2:1:0</code></a>, but in actuality it amounted to nothing more than a few scattered paragraphs split across a few scattered “drafts”.  There’s nothing of substance there.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
		<includes>
