		<includes>
	<Volume rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::3:7">
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="./3/7/"/>
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:3:7"/>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">7</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">Welcome to Earth</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>From the original project notes:</p>
	<blockquote>
		<p>Humans move to a new planet, name it Earth after their original planet. It is in the <strong style="Font-Weight: Inherit; Text-Transform: Uppercase">Ice Age</strong> and humans are forced to take a step back in evolution if they are to survive.</p>
	</blockquote>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
		
	</Volume>
		</includes>
		<includes>
	<Volume rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::3:6">
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="./3/6/"/>
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:3:6"/>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">6</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">Explosion</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>From the original project notes:</p>
	<blockquote>
		<p>The Sun is going to blow, threatening the survival of the human race.</p>
	</blockquote>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
		
	</Volume>
		</includes>
		<includes>
	<Volume rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::3:1">
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="./3/1/"/>
		<owl:sameAs rdf:resource="#bjmns:3:1"/>
		<identifier rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#NCName">rylie</identifier>
		<index rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</index>
		<fullTitle xml:lang="en">In the Palm of My Hand</fullTitle>
		<dc:abstract rdf:parseType="Resource">
			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
	<p>From the original project notes (revised):</p>
	<blockquote>
		<h1 style="Margin-Block: 0 1.25EM; Margin-Inline: 0; Border: None; Padding: 0; Font: Inherit; Text-Align: Start; Text-Align-Last: Auto; Text-Decoration: Underline">The Story of Rylielectronics</h1>
		<ul>
			<li>I.U. starts “chip project”.</li>
			<li>Adjusts power lines to only give power to Rylielectronics; would take other products and make them compatible. (Also added chip!)</li>
			<li>chip instaled..</li>
			<li>chip (&amp; me) sustained for gov. purposes.</li>
		</ul>
	</blockquote>
	<p>See also <a href="https://go.KIBI.family/Corpora/bjmns.tumblr.com,2013/8/1/0/3/" resource="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::8:1:0:3"><code>bjmns:8:1:0:3</code></a>.</p>
</div></contents>
		</dc:abstract>
		<includes>
	<Version rdf:about="tag:bjmns.tumblr.com,2013:bns::3:1:0">
